title: Jobs search
description: Performs a search in Trade Me Jobs.

enum.name: xml
enum.description: Serialize responses into XML.

enum.name: json
enum.description: Serialize responses into JSON.

query.name: category
query.description: The ID of the category to search within (should be within the Jobs category). Searching within mulitple categories is supported; separate each category ID with a comma.

query.name: date_from
query.description: Excludes listings starting before this date.

query.name: district
query.description: The ID of a district to search within.

query.name: member_listing
query.description: Filters the listings to only those with the given seller.

query.name: page
query.description: The page number of the set of results to return, starting from 1. Defaults to 1.

query.name: photo_size
query.description: The size of the images to return in the results. Defaults to Thumbnail.

query.name: region
query.description: Specifies the ID of the region to search within. Note that there are multiple region lists, this parameter accepts a jobs region ID. Region IDs can be retrieved via this endpoint

query.name: return_did_you_mean
query.description: If the search string is typed incorrectly return a suggested correction.

query.name: rows
query.description: The number of results per page; also the maximum number of results to return. The maximum is 25 for unauthenticated requests and 500 for authenticated requests. Defaults to 25 (unauthenticated) or 50 (authenticated).

query.name: search_string
query.description: One or more keywords to use in a search query.

query.name: snap_parameters
query.description: Extract attributes from the search keywords and perform an attribute search

query.name: sort_order
query.description: Sorts the returned results using the specified sort order.

query.name: type
query.description: Type of position. Applicable values are "CT" (contract), "PT" (part time), "FT" (full time).

fields.name: TotalCount
fields.description: The total number of results in the collection. Can be larger than the number of returned results.

fields.name: TotalCountTruncated
fields.description: True if the total count of results exceeded the allowed maximum and was truncated.

fields.name: Page
fields.description: The index of the current page of results (starts at 1).

fields.name: PageSize
fields.description: The number of results in the current page.

fields.name: List
fields.description: A list of the results in the current page.
